snippet: Angelique Kerber's upset win over Serena Williams at the Australian Open and Milos Raonic's second Grand Slam semifinal appearance will ensure they're the biggest movers among top players in projected rankings to be released this week....
lead_paragraph: Angelique Kerber's upset win over Serena Williams at the Australian Open and Milos Raonic's second Grand Slam semifinal appearance will ensure they're the biggest movers among top players in projected rankings to be released this week.

headline.print_headline: Kerber, Raonic Biggest Rankings Movers After Australian Open
headline.main: Kerber, Raonic Biggest Rankings Movers After Australian Open
